<collectionCode box="[380,417,260,281]" country="Brazil" name="Servico de Microbiologia e Imunologia" pageId="12" pageNumber="119">LE</collectionCode>
, but did not find the isotype cited by Hawkes &amp; Hjerting as being in 
<collectionCode box="[618,673,290,311]" country="Russia" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15563" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15563" name="N. I. Vavilov Institute of Plant Industry" pageId="12" pageNumber="119" type="Herbarium">WIR</collectionCode>
; subsequent searches have also failed to reveal this specimen.
</paragraph>
